# Augustus
Augustus will be a muted-purple [[Dragon|dragon]], bonded to [[Versailles Silverblade|Versailles Silverblade]]. His egg was one of those that the [[King Pirphal|Sorcerer King]] had his [[Fallen Riders|Fallen Riders]] steal from [[Vroengard|Vroengard]] years ago.
